beer.beer_description:
Birthday Suit, we couldn’t not include a Hazy Double IPA in our birthday release as well as a not so subtle reference to the way a few of us are drinking at the moment, fitting for the current times.⁠
⁠
Big low temp whirlpool additions of Galaxy. Then we doubled down on the Mosaic and paired it with Nelson Sauvin for both dry hops. We’ve been saving a particular batch of Mosaic for this beer; we hope you enjoy it as much as we do.⁠
⁠
Best drunk on the couch in your birthday suit.⁠
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
